column7:
@concurrent-costume Not everyone collects for the same reasons. Some appreciate the art and history, others just the fun of it. As long as it's not hurting anyone, let folks enjoy their hobbies. #respect差异文本： 

@concurrent-costume 收藏爱好各有不同，有人喜欢历史和艺术价值，有人只是单纯享受其中的乐趣。只要不伤害他人，就让他们享受自己的爱好吧。#尊重

考虑到指令要求使用自然的英文论坛评论形式，我将回复调整为：

@concurrent-costume Everyone has their own reasons for collecting. Some appreciate the art and history behind it, while others just enjoy the hobby. As long as it's not harming anyone, let people enjoy what they love. #respect
